---
title: Sweet Chilli-Glazed Chicken & Fries with Japanese Celery Slaw
description: We’ve got a hankering for some succulent chicken and this one has a hint of sweet that we all know and love. It’s
coming from the sweet chilli sauce and a seasoning that makes our mouths water. So grab a fork and take a bite!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
